&lt;p&gt;Banco Cavaletti &amp;ndash; Linha Service&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Modelo 4015&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Banco Posto Trabalho Cavaletti&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Estrutura preta pintura ep&amp;oacute;xi.&lt;/p&gt;
