&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; line-height: 24px; color: #555555;&quot;&gt;PLATAFORMA DE TRABALHO WORK PRO &amp;ndash; 2009, vem com Prateleira ou divis&amp;oacute;ria Central Frontais,al&amp;eacute;m de ser linda e moderna para seu escrit&amp;oacute;rio ficar super organizado e atual&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 style=&quot;margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: inherit; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: inherit; font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;DESCRI&amp;Ccedil;&amp;Atilde;O&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; line-height: 24px; color: #555555;&quot;&gt;Ent&amp;atilde;o, os Tampos princial e central: constitu&amp;iacute;do em MDP 25mm com revestimento melam&amp;iacute;nico BP. Acabamento das bordas em fita de borda 2,00mm.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; line-height: 24px; color: #555555;&quot;&gt;Ent&amp;atilde;o, a Estrutura: Confeccionada em tubo de a&amp;ccedil;o carbono 40&amp;times;40 e 70&amp;times;70 e chapa estampadas e dobradas.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; line-height: 24px; color: #555555;&quot;&gt;Ent&amp;atilde;o, o Biombo Divisor Suspenso Frontal: Confeccionado em MDP (opcional tamb&amp;eacute;m em vidro liso ou jateado)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; line-height: 24px; color: #555555;&quot;&gt;Ent&amp;atilde;o, o Biombo Divisor Lateral: Confeccionado em MDP em diversas op&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es de cores.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; line-height: 24px; color: #555555;&quot;&gt;Ent&amp;atilde;o, o Gaveteiro volante: opciopal&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; line-height: 24px; color: #555555;&quot;&gt;Ent&amp;atilde;o, a Cor da Estrutura: alum&amp;iacute;nio, preto, branco, cristal(platina), argila, ovo, azul e grafite.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; line-height: 24px; color: #555555;&quot;&gt;Ent&amp;atilde;o, o acabamento: em pintura eletrost&amp;aacute;tica a p&amp;oacute; com tratamento antiferruginoso.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; line-height: 24px; color: #555555;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;Acompanha:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; line-height: 24px; color: #555555;&quot;&gt;Calha para fia&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o, tampa em alum&amp;iacute;nio com acesso a 4 pontos de energia e 4 pontos de&amp;nbsp;rede.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; line-height: 24px; color: #555555;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; line-height: 24px; color: #555555;&quot;&gt;**Diversas Op&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es: Tamanhos, Cores&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; line-height: 24px; color: #555555;&quot;&gt;**Diversas cores&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; line-height: 24px; color: #555555;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;Instru&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es de Limpeza:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; line-height: 24px; color: #555555;&quot;&gt;Ent&amp;atilde;o, passar um pano levemente umedecido com &amp;aacute;gua ou detergente neutro e em seguida um pano seco para as limpezas do dia a dia.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; line-height: 24px; color: #555555;&quot;&gt;Portanto, nunca use produtos abrasivos, como sapon&amp;aacute;ceos, esponja de a&amp;ccedil;o, escova com cerdas duras, entre outros.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; line-height: 24px; color: #555555;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; line-height: 24px; color: #555555;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;Instru&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es de Conserva&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; line-height: 24px; color: #555555;&quot;&gt;Evitar expor/utilizar os produtos em ambientes com alta umidade, exemplo: c&amp;acirc;maras frias, saunas e &amp;aacute;reas molhadas.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; line-height: 24px; color: #555555;&quot;&gt;N&amp;atilde;o armazenar produtos corrosivos, exemplo: &amp;aacute;cido, cloro etc.&lt;/p&gt;
